## Relation to `BHT_amyloid/`

| Old file | Replacement |
|----------|-------------|
| `arch_cross_...ipynb` | `amyloid-parse` / `scripts/parse_predictor.py` |
| `path_converter.py` | `amyloid-parse path` (+ APR export stays in legacy script) |
| `appnn_converter.R` | R runner → `amyloid-parse appnn` |
| `all/visualize.py` | reads `*_all.csv` from `--legacy` merge |
